# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:13
translate spanish jamietv2_fd039b16:

    # "I walk up to Jamie's door and knock."
    "me acerco a la puerta de Jamie y llamo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:14
translate spanish jamietv2_fdad75c4:

    # "I wait a bit for her to answer and after a few moments, I almost walk away thinking that she isn't home or is busy or something."
    "Espero un poco a que me responda y, al cabo de unos instantes, casi me voy pensando que no está en casa o que está ocupada o algo así."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:19
translate spanish jamietv2_56b288a0:

    # "Then, just when I am about to leave, she opens the door."
    "Entonces, justo cuando estoy a punto de marcharme, abre la puerta."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:20
translate spanish jamietv2_348b659c:

    # gnd "Hey sorry, I must have fell asleep on the couch."
    gnd "Oye, lo siento, me debo de haber quedado dormida en el sofá."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:21
translate spanish jamietv2_85e15039:

    # pc "Oh I'm sorry, I didn't mean to wake you. Was just wondering if you wanted to hang out?"
    pc "Oh, lo siento, no era mi intención despertarte. Solo me preguntaba si te apetecía pasar un rato juntos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:22
translate spanish jamietv2_8cddc873:

    # gnd "Sure, want to come watch TV with me?"
    gnd "Claro, ¿quieres venir a ver la tele conmigo?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:23
translate spanish jamietv2_6eafa1e5:

    # pc "Are you sure? You look pretty tired."
    pc "¿Estás segura? Pareces bastante cansada."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:24
translate spanish jamietv2_d5f53ad3:

    # gnd "I'm exhausted, but I'd still like to spend some time with you."
    gnd "Estoy agotada, pero aún así me gustaría pasar un rato contigo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:25
translate spanish jamietv2_35743d5e:

    # pc "Okay then."
    pc "Vale, entonces."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:26
translate spanish jamietv2_d6443097:

    # "We walk inside and sit down on her couch to watch TV together."
    "Entramos y nos sentamos en su sofá para ver la tele juntos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:29
translate spanish jamietv2_4eefcd41:

    # pc "You not been sleeping well?"
    pc "¿No has estado durmiendo bien?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:30
translate spanish jamietv2_d3a1e5f8:

    # gnd "I've just been studying a lot. It's been tough."
    gnd "Es que he estado estudiando mucho. Ha sido duro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:31
translate spanish jamietv2_6d7e76b4:

    # pc "Tell me about it."
    pc "Y que lo digas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:32
translate spanish jamietv2_56872787:

    # gnd "But I'm glad to spend some time with you, even if I'm sleepy."
    gnd "Pero me alegro de pasar un rato contigo, aunque tenga sueño."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:37
translate spanish jamietv2_c7a75159:

    # gnd "Are you implying I'm not cute when I'm not sleepy?"
    gnd "¿Estás insinuando que no soy guapa cuando no tengo sueño?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:38
translate spanish jamietv2_4db958a5:

    # pc "What? No."
    pc "¿Qué? No."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:39
translate spanish jamietv2_cf0825c6:

    # gnd "I'm just kidding. Thanks, you're sweet."
    gnd "Solo bromeaba. Gracias, eres un encanto."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:42
translate spanish jamietv2_175d3768:

    # gnd "What? Are you serious?"
    gnd "¿Qué? ¿Lo dices en serio?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:43
translate spanish jamietv2_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:44
translate spanish jamietv2_f3a7bdd3:

    # gnd "That's probably not a good idea. My dad might actually kill you."
    gnd "Probablemente no sea una buena idea. Mi padre podría matarte."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:45
translate spanish jamietv2_796397b3:

    # pc "It might be worth the risk."
    pc "Quizá valga la pena correr el riesgo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:46
translate spanish jamietv2_34f266ea:

    # gnd "You're crazy!"
    gnd "¡Estás loco!"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:49
translate spanish jamietv2_d13864ee:

    # gnd "But no, let's just watch TV."
    gnd "Pero no, mejor veamos la tele."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:52
translate spanish jamietv2_8105064d:

    # "She smiles at me and we both turn towards the TV and watch the show."
    "Me sonríe y los dos nos giramos hacia la tele y vemos el programa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:55
translate spanish jamietv2_e4b4fe92:

    # "After the first commercial break, I hear her snoring softly and a moment later, she leans over and lays her head on my shoulder."
    "Tras la primera pausa publicitaria, la oigo roncar suavemente y, un momento después, se inclina y apoya la cabeza en mi hombro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:56
translate spanish jamietv2_72d126bc:

    # "I sit there like that, feeling her warm weight against me, smelling the scent of her shampoo. It's nice."
    "Me quedo ahí sentado, sintiendo su cálido peso contra mí, oliendo el aroma de su champú. Es agradable."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:57
translate spanish jamietv2_a7276863:

    # "I watch the rest of the show, letting her sleep on my shoulder until the credits roll."
    "Veo el resto del programa, dejándola dormir sobre mi hombro hasta que aparecen los créditos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:60
translate spanish jamietv2_aced7ae5:

    # "The music playing during the credits wakes her and she opens her eyes and looks up at me, putting her hand on my chest."
    "La música que suena durante los créditos la despierta y ella abre los ojos y me mira, poniendo su mano sobre mi pecho."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:61
translate spanish jamietv2_222fe902:

    # gnd "Oh man, I missed the whole thing."
    gnd "Ay, tío, me lo he perdido todo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:62
translate spanish jamietv2_7289beae:

    # pc "Yeah, I'll have to fill you in later."
    pc "Sí, tendré que ponerte al día más tarde."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:63
translate spanish jamietv2_d912edc5:

    # gnd "You could have woke me up."
    gnd "Podrías haberme despertado."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:66
translate spanish jamietv2_fd8175bb:

    # gnd "I definitely did."
    gnd "Claro que lo hice."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:68
translate spanish jamietv2_7b910158:

    # gnd "You're so silly."
    gnd "Eres tan tonto."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:69
translate spanish jamietv2_d404c590:

    # gnd "Do you really think I'm cute?"
    gnd "¿De verdad crees que soy mona?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:70
translate spanish jamietv2_2951ed74:

    # pc "Definitely."
    pc "Por supuesto."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:71
translate spanish jamietv2_d2d7ae9c:

    # gnd "I think you're cute too."
    gnd "Yo también creo que eres mona."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:72
translate spanish jamietv2_e8e9a7f7:

    # "Once again, her dad picks the worst moment to open the door and walk in."
    "Una vez más, su padre elige el peor momento para abrir la puerta y entrar."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:73
translate spanish jamietv2_9da07a83:

    # "Jamie leans away from me and stands up."
    "Jamie se aparta de mí y se pone de pie."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:79
translate spanish jamietv2_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_011.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_011.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:80
translate spanish jamietv2_25b98dfa:

    # gnd "Hey, Daddy."
    gnd "Hola, papá."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:81
translate spanish jamietv2_20dcad47:

    # jd "Send him home."
    jd "Mándalo a casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:82
translate spanish jamietv2_f2596c67:

    # "Her dad doesn't say anything else and instead walks past us and into the kitchen."
    "Su padre no dice nada más y, en lugar de eso, pasa junto a nosotros y se dirige a la cocina."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:86
translate spanish jamietv2_84d4365c:

    # gnd "He must have had a bad day."
    gnd "Debe de haber tenido un mal día."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:87
translate spanish jamietv2_b44cf649:

    # pc "I should probably go."
    pc "Probablemente debería irme."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:88
translate spanish jamietv2_a6870bf2:

    # gnd "Yeah, I'm sorry."
    gnd "Sí, lo siento."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:89
translate spanish jamietv2_b219d344:

    # pc "It's okay."
    pc "No pasa nada."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:92
translate spanish jamietv2_36b8ae4f:

    # gnd "Thanks for coming over tonight. I had a good time."
    gnd "Gracias por venir esta noche. Me lo he pasado bien."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:93
translate spanish jamietv2_041dfd87:

    # pc "More like you had a good nap."
    pc "Más bien te has echado una buena siesta."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:94
translate spanish jamietv2_b762e00f:

    # gnd "That too. Your shoulder is very comfy."
    gnd "Eso también. Tu hombro es muy cómodo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:98
translate spanish jamietv2_4bbcc4b9:

    # gnd "I might take you up on that."
    gnd "Puede que te haga caso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:100
translate spanish jamietv2_f9097bdf:

    # gnd "I'm sure they'll show re-runs all week."
    gnd "Seguro que pondrán reposiciones toda la semana."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:101
translate spanish jamietv2_dfc3c586:

    # pc "Alright, well I better head home."
    pc "Vale, pues mejor me voy a casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:103
translate spanish jamietv2_ecb1e778:

    # gnd "Okay, [pcname]. See you again soon."
    gnd "Vale, [pcname]. Nos vemos pronto."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:104
translate spanish jamietv2_209b1712:

    # pc "See ya."
    pc "Nos vemos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:105
translate spanish jamietv2_1557defd:

    # "With that, she goes back inside and I walk back over to my house."
    "Con eso, ella vuelve a entrar y yo me dirijo de nuevo a mi casa."

